---
title: Peri Peri Chorizo and Chicken Breast Traybake with Roast Potatoes and Tomato & Pea Shoot Salad
description: Perfect for kids and grown-ups alike, this Peri Peri Chorizo and Chicken Breast Traybake is sure to become a new family favourite. Our easy tips and tweaks will help you create a dish that's to everyone's tastes! For little ones, keep some chicken plain without the spice and set aside the salad before adding the dressing.
